social_posts.post_text: Congratulations to DC on a BIG win tonight. I got caught by a good shot. I may not like his crew very much but cannot take away from his victory. Time to get back to the gym. 🙏🏼🙏🏼💯

Post fight thoughts- Sometimes in life thing just don’t go your way… Even when you prepare relentlessly and are on point. Training along with some of the best in the game… You can still get knocked down. It may seem cliche but it truly is about getting BACK UP…  So it’s back to grind this Monday morning! I dropped 60lbs in 8 weeks for this last one because I DID NOT STAY READY… A lesson for the younger fighters out there, use me as an example. I know I am one of the best HW out there but if you do not dedicate every minute to your craft, you just may find yourself playing catch-up (like I did). I believe I have so much more in the tank and plan on showing it soon. Thank you ALL for the love and support and even the haters because without you… There’s no Hammer!! God Bless Proverbs 16:3
Drop a birthday wish in the comments for the Hammer Josh Burns.
No matter how it’s going… KEEP GOING… Pursue the unbelievable life because 99% settle for a believable one.💯 ⚒️⚒️⚒️⚒️#hammerhouse4life

Picked up this random at the wedding… Should be a good night. 😉

social_posts.post_text: A recap on this past Thursday night fights!! Man what a Great War @levi_pitbull had! Went all 5 rounds this is a clip that I liked 😂 ( he put me on my butt twice) BUT this was right after he got me down and I was able to return the favor. 😂. At this point in my career I just love a good fight with an awesome warrior! Thank you to @bybextreme and my team @chrisgoldengloves and @knuckleuppodcast. This is what bareknuckle fights are about blood, heart and the passion to compete!! It was an absolute honor to share the trigon with Levi and look forward to doing again soon. Thank you to @dphhr @coachtoughill @melmatchmaker @bloomgreg @official.bigmo and last but not least the MAN himself @bybmike !!! I absolutely feel like family at BYB and know I’ve found my home. They treated my fiancé @gypsy_cals94 and my lil man “Gman” like family as well. I could go on and on but man what an absolute incredible night!! Love all of you for the support and look forward to my next fight that’s in the works right now and TRUST ME…. You don’t wanna miss this one!!! 💪🏼💪🏼💯
